<paragraph blockId="37.[151,1437,151,2013]" box="[199,1092,1698,1725]" pageId="37" pageNumber="38">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,411,1698,1725]" pageId="37" pageNumber="38">Taxonomic Notes.</emphasis>
This species was included in 
<bibRefCitation author="Cannings, R. A." box="[745,933,1699,1725]" pageId="37" pageNumber="38" refId="ref107923" refString="Cannings, R. A. (2002) The Systematics of Lasiopogon (Diptera: Asilidae). Royal British Columbia Museum, Victoria, British Columbia, 354 pp." type="book" year="2002">Cannings (2002)</bibRefCitation>
